JSTL first search “JSTL download” open https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/javax.servlet/jstl/1.2 and click on jar file and download it
Now create dynamic web project  and put this downloaded jar to webcontentwebinflib and past within lib. We will also build the path for the project and add 2 jar files from tomcat apache
1.	Servlet-api.jar
2.	Jsp-api.jar
It JSTL we have 5 kind of taglib
i.	Core Tag  <%@ taglib prefix="c" uri="http://java.sun.com/jsp/jstl/core"%>
ii.	XML Tag
iii.	SQL Tag
iv.	JSTL Functions
v.	Formatting Tags
